00:26:05,059 --> 00:26:05,759
And we made a demo.

406
00:26:06,119 --> 00:26:10,441
You could fly around in space and grab asteroids and do neat things.

407
00:26:11,401 --> 00:26:15,302
And it was a very rudimentary prototype.

408
00:26:15,482 --> 00:26:18,143
You had to be careful not to make it fall apart as you were playing with it.

409
00:26:19,423 --> 00:26:21,824
But we started to show it to some people.

410
00:26:22,724 --> 00:26:24,345
And it was really, really cool.

411
00:26:24,365 --> 00:26:25,185
They'd come and play it.

412
00:26:26,065 --> 00:26:28,746
And people started filling in all of the missing parts.

413
00:26:29,426 --> 00:26:30,627
I didn't play that video with audio.

414
00:26:30,647 --> 00:26:31,587
But people started coming.

415
00:26:32,467 --> 00:26:36,230
You know, adding in, they'd make their own sound effects and they'd come and, you know,

416
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:38,992
pshew, whoosh.

