00:27:20,447 --> 00:27:21,388
You're doing this all wrong.

429
00:27:23,272 --> 00:27:23,892
This is horrible.

430
00:27:25,133 --> 00:27:25,673
I can fix it.

431
00:27:27,394 --> 00:27:29,615
And he said, I have to show you something.

432
00:27:30,236 --> 00:27:31,316
And so we went to see.

433
00:27:32,297 --> 00:27:39,141
And Vlad had scratch built this custom drone with head

